General.Name: Haranga Resources Ltd
General.Description: Haranga Resources Limited explores and develops gold and uranium assets in West Africa. The company holds interests in a range of gold projects located in Cote d'Ivoire and Burkina Faso; and a uranium project in Senegal. Haranga Resources Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Victoria Park, Australia.
